snippet.title: [Favorite Horror Game #3] Best VGM 1671 - Resident Evil REmake - Guardhouse I
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 738 - https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pOK5gWEnEPY

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Gamecube / Wii
Resident Evil REmake (2002)
Guardhouse I
Misao Senbongi & Makoto Tomozawa
